liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: It's a hattrick for Nicolas Jackson! He had Mudryk alongside him, but the Ukrainian strayed offside, so Jackson shifted the ball away from Vicario, who is sat on his backside, and Jackson strokes the ball into the empty net.
liveBlogPostPrepared.title: 90+7' GOAL CHELSEA!

children.content: It's a hattrick for Nicolas Jackson!
He had Mudryk alongside him, but the Ukrainian strayed offside, so Jackson shifted the ball away from Vicario, who is sat on his backside, and Jackson strokes the ball into the empty net.
